{"tid":968880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國人組團到泰國當乞衣 不給錢即大罵","createTime":"2019-01-04T15:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:35:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47f9cc6b5995353f76e5346739975a58ac187b0b","tid":968880,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"中國6名男子非法進入泰國乞討，並沿街騷擾民眾，目前已遭到警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n根據《泰國網》，中國6名殘疾男子，於去年底持旅遊簽證前入泰國，藏身在曼谷素鐵訕附近的飯店里。他們夜晚便會待在飯店裡，白天就會前往分頭曼谷的知名旅遊景點四處乞討，傍晚再回飯店。<br />\n<br />\n泰國警方為了逮捕他們，出動了大批警力，並經過縝密的規劃於去年12月27日將其6人逮捕。警方表示，這群丐幫中年齡最大的46歲，最小21歲。他們平均一天至少能乞討到3000泰銖（約2874新台幣），不過每天要上繳1000泰銖（約958新台幣）給丐幫頭子。<br />\n<br />\n在泰國，未經許可乞討將面臨最高一個月監禁或罰款。這6人以非法乞討、外籍人員非法入境、逾期滯留泰國等罪名，遭警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n中國乞丐前往泰國的現象，早在今年7月就已出現，當時一名雙腿萎縮的老人，不斷騷擾路邊民眾，只要不給錢就會破口大罵，儘管遭到驅趕也死纏爛打，直到警方到場才肯離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2662381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2662381&d=VDOKtd8IA5ycP%2BmwAMRj69tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=43e219ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2662381&h=1dc9b138\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2662381</a>"},{"pid":"a04b13dfdee6019e3f601d8e99dc52a985098508","tid":968880,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20170128/720pix/1485544852_05ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170128%2F720pix%2F1485544852_05ef.jpg&h=cdb53ced&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1870ad94bf559abbb1dcbc0e1c5edf1684722d88","tid":968880,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58e682554b4d644fc5b3403163bb7266f11565d","tid":968880,"uid":59695,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"支那人去邊都係做乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31e7d00ee00c5da64b31c6ca4b00cffcb578aab","tid":968880,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a04b13dfdee6019e3f601d8e99dc52a985098508","tid":968880,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20170128/720pix/1485544852_05ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170128%2F720pix%2F1485544852_05ef.jpg&h=cdb53ced&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T22:51:15.000Z","msg":"呢個真係經典, 慈禧再世."},{"pid":"827347d42e98dce951c8e6e1bdbed443f501f5a2","tid":968880,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T00:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e9d04f62057bbee2dd9bc0f3eeda9cfcb76d09","tid":968880,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb49a424376b48df3aa974bf062a19a263c91e8","tid":968880,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"天生乞衣dna"},{"pid":"60431933219091c78494944323c0a554d3611b9b","tid":968880,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04b13dfdee6019e3f601d8e99dc52a985098508","tid":968880,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20170128/720pix/1485544852_05ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170128%2F720pix%2F1485544852_05ef